Alert slide 
=========================
type: alert 
incremental: true
transition: fade

This is a *alert* slide with 
- **incremental** set to *true*,
- **transition** set to *fade*.

This is an example of *numbered* list:

1. item 1
2. item 2
3. item 3


Slide without title and different fonts
=========================
title: false
type: exclaim

This slide has
- **title** set to *false* 
- **type** set to *exclaim* 

with 
```css
.exclaim .reveal .state-background {
  background: black;
} 

.exclaim .reveal div {
  color: white;
  font-family: 'Lacquer';
}

.exclaim .reveal code {
  color: red;
  font-family: 'Lacquer';
}
```

